          <h1 class="signature" translate="no">world_list(Hosts)<span class="signature-arrow">&nbsp;≡&nbsp;</span><span class="signature-result">world_list(Hosts, silent)</span></h1>


            <a href="https://github.com/erlang/otp/blob/master/lib/kernel/src/net_adm.erl#L270" class="icon-action" rel="help nofollow" aria-label="View Source">
              <i class="ri-code-s-slash-line" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </a>

